<main id="main-content">
    <section id="hero">
        <div class="jumbotron" id="banner">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 col-sm-10 col-md-7">
                        <h3>A Procurement Haulage & Logistics Company</h3>
                        <p class="lead">We creatively move products with our smart
                            supply chain management and operations.
                        </p>
                        <a href="meet_us" class="btn outline">Meet us now<span class="fa fa-angle-right ml-2"></span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="mid">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <figure class="col-12 mx-auto petrol-tools">
                  <img src="images/petrol_tools.png" class="img-fluid">
                </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                    <h4>Sales of Petroleum products</h4>
                    <p>We sell petroleum products such as PMS, AGO,
                    DPK and LPG at affordable prices. Apart from
                    prompt delivery, our products are of high industrial quality. We also
                    offer retail services to end users of petroleum products as 
                    our fuel stations at several locations within the Niger Delta 
                    enclave are fully equipped with powerful pumping machines,
                     calibrated meters manned by a team of well drilled staffs.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                    <h4>General contractors</h4>
                    <p>At Onaidjuku we undertake contracts including supply of 
                    merchandise to offshore sites. We also manage and finance 
                    projects upon  successful study and project analysis.
                    Other projects we undergo includes constructions of roads, 
                    maintanance services.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                    <h4>Haulage procurement and Logistics</h4>
                    <p>Within our mission lies the desire to bridge the 
                        gap between the refineries and consumers of petroleum products. Within our offices 
                        in several locations in the Niger Delta, are ranges of 
                        oil haulage trucks and tankers to move products to places 
                        of consumption(filling stations, telecom sites and company plants).
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="operations">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
               <div class="col-12 col-sm-4 col-md-5">
                  <% include carousel %>
               </div>
               <div class="col-12 col-sm-5 col-md-5">
                 <h5 class="text-center">Welcome to Onaidjuku Nig. Enterprises</h5>
                 <p>ONAIDJUKU NIG ENT. is a Procurement, Haulage and Transportation company, registered under the corporate affairs commission, and 
                     having its head office in Delta state Nigeria. We deal in various products and services including AGO, 
                     PMS, DPK and others. our services also includes Bunkering and General contractors.
                 </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-8 col-sm-3 col-md-2 mx-auto">
                    <div class="">
